{
  "name": "SparkAxes",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.SparklineGroup\">SparklineGroup</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparklineGroup/SparklineGroup .htm#SparklineGroup.Axes\">Axes</a></strong> 属性可返回该组迷你图的 <strong>SparkAxes</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组是否按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightToLeftPlotOrder</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的水平轴的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axis</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>表示一组迷你图的水平轴和垂直轴的设置。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Horizontal",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkAxes/SparkAxes .htm#SparkAxes.SparkAxes\">SparkAxes</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SparkHorizontalAxis/SparkHorizontalAxis .htm#SparkHorizontalAxis.SparkHorizontalAxis\">SparkHorizontalAxis</a></strong> 对象。只读</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组设置为按右至左顺序在水平轴上绘制点。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sparklineGroup = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    sparklineGroup.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RightToLeftPlotOrder</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格 H1 中第一个迷你图组的迷你图的水平轴是否基于日期值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shAxis = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;H1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SparklineGroups</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Axes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Horizontal</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shAxis.<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsDateAxis</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "<p><strong>SparkHorizontalAxis</strong></p>\n",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
